name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Fast and the Furious Quotes New Tab

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds your favorite quotes from the Fast and the Furious franchise to your new tab page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you love the Fast and the Furious franchise, this will help you remember your favorite moments. 

Read Dom's inspirational speeches, Tyrese's jokes and much more.

There are over 300 unique quotes that are randomly picked each time you open a new tab.

Extension is easy to use, there is nothing to setup, just install and you are ready to go.
